PACOMMON=%BRAND Toolbar - It's NEW, it's FREE, it's COOL. Check out all it's functions. Enhances your browsing experience with many cool features. No spyware, no adware, no viruses.
COMMON=Use powerful search tool with Yahoo or MSN search engine. Search for music, images, news and all you need right from your desktop.
COMMON=Popup Blocker - Stop annoying popups. Don't let popups disrupt your browsing experience. View only popups you want to see. Control your browsing.
COMMON=Yellow Pages - Find any business faster than ever. Search by name or category, within your state or the whole United States. Get the information you need right on your desktop.
COMMON=Form Filler - Save your time online. Don't waste your time by filling out the web forms. Let the Form Filler do it for you.
COMMON=Games - Play FREE online games. Don't ever get bored again. Pick a game and start playing now.
COMMON=Skins - Change your Internet Explorer appearance. Replace the boring grey design by a colorful skin of your choice.
MAIL=Email Notifier - Monitor multiple Inbox, Gmail, Yahoo, Hotmail & POP3 email accounts. Get notifications about incoming messages in System tray.
WEATHER=Weather - Get the weather information right on your desktop. Monitor your local weather forecast or check weather anywhere in the world.
RADIO=Radio & MP3 Player - Listen to radio & MP3 while browsing the internet. Record your favorite radio shows and listen to them whenever you want.
WSG=Web Security Guard - Keep your privacy private. Alerts you to unauthorized changes of your security settings. Erases the traces of your computer activities.
RSS=RSS Reader - Get online breaking world news from CNN, BBC, CBS, ABC, CNET and other news services on your Internet Explorer. Get RSS feeds on your desktop.
SSAVER=Wallpapers - Download our unique wallpapers from our picture gallery. Download as many wallpapers as you want and change your desktop anytime you want just like clothes!
SSAVER=Screensavers - Download FREE 3D & Slideshow screensavers. Turn your desktop into a Marine Aquarium or Fireplace. Create your screensaver of your favorite pictures.
SAV_3DAQUARIUM=3D Aquarium Screensaver - FREE 3D Marine & Tropical Aquarium turns your PC into a wonderful 3D sea aquarium. Watch the incredible sea life of dolphins, sharks and orcas!
SAV_3DEARTH=3D Earth Screensaver - Fly around the planet Earth and zoom on any place on it. Witness hurricanes & storms the way only astronauts do! View the local time and weather forecast!
SAV_3DFIREPLACE=3D Fireplace Screensaver - Drive out the winter chill with our FREE Fireplace Screensavers! Hear the realistic sounds of flames!
COMMON=Animated Cursors - Change your cursor from boring black and white arrow pointer and choose from over 500 different colorful mouse pointers and animated cursors to energize your mouse.
COMMON=Download Manager - Download files fast & easy. Manage downloads using Download Queue. Set the number of simultaneous downloads. Email large files quickly, securely and easily.
